    • Class de.gnwi.psmilesviewer.UserPreferences extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • cssNodeColor

          java.awt.Color cssNodeColor
          The graph's node color as set in the stylesheet.

        • cssNodeShapeKey

          java.lang.String cssNodeShapeKey

        • currentNodeColor

          java.awt.Color currentNodeColor
          The current node color as set by the user or the stylesheet (after a reset).

        • currentNodeShapeKey

          java.lang.String currentNodeShapeKey
          The current node shape key as set by the user or the stylesheet (after a reset). It must be able to be found in the Constants.Shape enum's gsKeys.

        • currentErrorColor

          java.awt.Color currentErrorColor
          The current error color as set by the user or Constants.DEFAULT_ERROR_COLOR (after a reset).

        • currentValidColor

          java.awt.Color currentValidColor
          The current 'valid' color as set by the user or Constants.DEFAULT_VALID_COLOR (after a reset).

        • currentNodeWeight

          java.lang.Double currentNodeWeight
          The current node weight as set by the user or Constants.DEFAULT_NODE_WEIGHT (after a reset).

        • currentEdgeWeight

          java.lang.Double currentEdgeWeight
          The current edge weight as set by the user or Constants.DEFAULT_NODE_WEIGHT (after a reset).

        • cssNodeSize

          int cssNodeSize
          The graph's node size as set in the stylesheet.

        • currentNodeSize

          int currentNodeSize
          The current node size as set by the user or the stylesheet (after a reset).

        • isFullParticleNameDisplay

          boolean isFullParticleNameDisplay
          Determines whether the particle names should be written out in full in the graph as set by the user or Constants.IS_FULL_PARTICLE_NAME_DISPLAY_DEFAULT (after a reset).

        • cssNodeSizeMode

          org.graphstream.ui.graphicGraph.stylesheet.StyleConstants.SizeMode cssNodeSizeMode
          The graph's node size mode as set by the stylesheet. Determines whether the node size can be set dynamically by the user (in case of DYN_SIZE) or if the nodes fit automatically to their labels (particle names) (in case of FIT).

        • imageFileDir

          java.lang.String imageFileDir
          The directory the user set to save the exported image files to.

        • stylesheet

          java.lang.String stylesheet
          The String representation of the css file added to the PSmiles graph as stylesheet.
